reviewText: If you like 80's porn you should like this movie from 85.  Lots of young starlets of the age, a bit of humor a even a little bit of plot.  The picture quality is not the best as it was taken from a tape and you can see an occasional flaw but it doesn't interfere with enjoying the show.

I have a huge thing for Jenna Jameson and am a huge fan. I also fine the whole "My Plaything" POV style very entertaining and stimulating. This however, is not what I was hoping for. Most of the scenes were not in the POV style and it came across as just another porno with selectable scenes.
The dvd was just what I was looking for. IF you want a nice mature movie you won't regret getting this product.
